item.title: Desperate Attempt at Restarting Journaling
item.description: It’s time to face itâ€”I feel like journaling is the one part of myself I consistently lie about. It’s the one thing I tell people I do, which in reality I fail to more often than not. It’s true, I used to journal a lot, and it’s done me lots of good. It’s even true that I actually enjoy journaling when I finally get around to it. I just struggle to get around to doing it and sticking to it.
